              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 1 pt de</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> DGT Hydro</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et invoque un</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">cercle de mélodie</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/35653081/6ce6beac71091e13fe09094e6af6b210_8727932727529225883.png",
                "id": "talent22899",
                "key": "C'est parti pour le show ♪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "C'est parti pour le show ♪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Soigne tous vos personnages pour 4 pts.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/35653081/bae3085f162716c905447f4c84f2bcf8_7926595409777895737.png",
                "id": "talent19267",
                "key": "Miracle brillant ♪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Miracle brillant ♪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Invocation</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase finale </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Soigne tous vos personnages pour 1 pt et </span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">applique l'élément Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> au personnage actif.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/35653081/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4773283048529073954.png",
                "id": "talent10064",
                "key": "Cercle de mélodie",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/35653081/2f913e4b976b65b1d93dd9a3606ce58a_3099070380491172238.png",
                "title": "Cercle de mélodie"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Hydro et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Évaporation : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Électrocution :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> DGT actuels +1 et inflige 1 pt de DGT de perforation à tous les personnages adverses autre que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Gel :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> DGT actuels +1 et immobilise la cible pendant la manche actuelle (Peut être annulé en avance subissant des DGT physiques ou Pyro, mais DGT +2)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Fleurissement :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> DGT actuels +1 et crée un</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">noyau Dendro</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">qui augmente le prochain coup de DGT Pyro/Électro de 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/35653081/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_8986075972101195508.png",
                "id": "talent22062",
                "key": "DGT Hydro",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Hydro"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Application Hydro</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Lorsque l'élément Hydro est appliqué sans infliger de DGT, la réaction élémentaire déclenchée ignore les effets de DGT :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Évaporation : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Aucun effet</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Électrocution : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Aucun effet</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Gel : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Immobilise la cible pendant la manche actuelle (Peut être annulé en avance subissant des DGT physiques ou Pyro, mais DGT +2)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Fleurissement : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Crée un </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">noyau Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> qui augmente le prochain coup de DGT Pyro/Électro de 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/35653081/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4434718640883923783.png",
